article:
This is an incomplete list of landmarks in Manhattan from 59th Street to 110th
Street designated by the New York City Landmark Preservation Commission. Some of
these are also National Historic Landmark (NHL) sites, and NHL status is noted
where known.

: source: [http://www.nyc.gov/html/lpc/html/forms/reports_man.shtml];
:[http://www.neighborhoodpreservationcenter.org/designation_reports/]; date
:listed is date of designation;

:see also: [[National Register of Historic Places listings in Manhattan from
59th to 110th Streets]]
